                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880625-12-off59 t17880625-12-cd60"></join>, one carcass of a dead sheep, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880625-12-victim176" type="victimName">
                     Francis 
                     Preston
                  <interp inst="t17880625-12-victim176" type="surname" value="Preston"></interp>
